steps.name: I am on the homePage "https://www.carsguide.com.au" of CarsGuide Website
I move to the menu
click on "SearchCars" link
select CarBrand as "BMW" from AnyMake dropDown
select Model as "1 SERIES" from Model dropDown
select Location as "Australia" from Location dropDown
select Price as "$1,000" from price dropDown
click on Find_My_Next_Car button
I should see list of SearchedCars
Page title should be "Bmw 1 Series Under 1000 for Sale | carsguide"

arguments.val: Bmw 1 Series Under 1000 for Sale | carsguide

steps.name: I am on the homePage "https://www.carsguide.com.au" of CarsGuide Website
I move to the menu
click on "UsedCarSearch" link on Used Car Search Page
select CarBrand as "AUDI" from AnyMake dropDown on Used Car Search Page
select car model on Used Car Search Page
select Model as "A6" from Model dropDown on Used Car Search Page
select Location as "Australia" from Location dropDown on Used Car Search Page
select Price as "$5,000" from price dropDown on Used Car Search Page
click on Find_My_Next_Car button on Used Car Search Page
I should see list of SearchedCars on Used Car Search Page
